instruction: Can you generate a list of 10 interesting things to do in New York City?
output:

2. Visit the Metropolitan Museum of Art
3. See Central Park
4. Take a walking tour of the Financial District
5. Explore the High Line
6. Take a ferry ride to Ellis Island
7. Visit the Brooklyn Botanic Garden
8. See a show on Broadway
9. Have a picnic in Central Park
10. Enjoy a day at Coney Island.
